title: Mr. Bankshot in the trap! with Karlous Miller, Clayton English and Navv Greene
itunes:title: Mr. Bankshot in the trap! with Karlous Miller, Clayton English and Navv Greene
description:
The hilarious stand-up comedian and internet content creator Mr. Bankshot is in the 85 South Show’s trap to get some laughs in with the crew. Jay- Z vs. Future? Everbody weighs in on who would win in a VERZUZ and they take a look back at some of their favorite FUTURE songs. Then Mr. Bankshot talks about his new provocative single he just released. It’s about people living on the “down low” and it’s started some controversy on the internets.
